No such plan in place as yet on student vaccination and prioritization.

Schools are currently closed primarily for the regular winter holidays. The holidays began earlier this year to avoid a surge due to the second wave of the pandemic. Final school examinations are due in the spring of 1400 solar calendar (March/April 2021). Efforts have been made to diversify education service delivery in response to the closure of educational institutions and such situations in the future. Online delivery alone is not feasible given the limited facilities. A mix of blended and online learning is recommended. No student group prioritization or vaccination has been made so far.
